{"tid":1856263,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"【武漢肺炎】民航處：越南復飛往來香港航班","createTime":"2020-02-01T13:56:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T16:07:23.000Z","uid":59919,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d6f46402a371b1cb24f5ef93da28ee0d7dc08d62","tid":1856263,"uid":59919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T13:56:49.000Z","msg":"【21:45】民航處發新聞稿，指特區政府知悉有關措施後積極與越南民航局聯絡跟進，並詳細解釋香港國際機場的防疫措施。越南民航局今日晚上取消有關措施。<br />\n【21:00】旅遊業議會總幹事陳張樂怡表示，就越南政府今日封關，現時有至少600名參加旅行團到當地旅遊的港人仍在越南<br />\n <a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200201&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=60548116\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200201%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D60548116&d=ANzGKs6Ysw%2B%2BKy1wioRXty%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=2c28df9d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200201%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D60548116&h=e68dc689\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200201&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=60548116</a>"},{"pid":"b9c60efa8a897814dcbc4d5be0e7768d819ffcc4","tid":1856263,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T13:57:48.000Z","msg":"港獨台獨"},{"pid":"3d247f00ba7e844f068825c2e830343deba10f3e","tid":1856263,"uid":272422,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T13:59:33.000Z","msg":"林奠政府帶頭岐視中國疫國<br />\n林奠要求越南對中國及香港作差別待遇<br />\n係背叛國家背叛黨嘅行為"},{"pid":"d56755d6d4eae05b363ba88643b802425684ea0d","tid":1856263,"uid":2189,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T14:31:21.000Z","msg":"Hong Kong is NOT China"},{"pid":"ad7dc6259e6df9bad331873532983eacca1fa84d","tid":1856263,"uid":279320,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d56755d6d4eae05b363ba88643b802425684ea0d","tid":1856263,"uid":2189,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T14:31:21.000Z","msg":"Hong Kong is NOT China"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T